  * Improve foreign content handling. This will fix CVE-2017-1000065 that was
    discovered by: Machaj Wojciech, Mariusz Sucajtys, Artur Wojtkowski,
    Marcin Kozłowski, Paweł Piekutowski, COMP S.A.
  * Adapt nginx SSL ciphers to latest intermediate profile according to
    https://mozilla.github.io/server-side-tls/ssl-config-generator.
  * Mantis 0001701: Switch back to NTP daemon.

