  * Update locales.
  * Various improvements and bugfixes.
  * Set 'obey pam restrictions = no' by default in smb.conf to force Samba
    to use the directory mode/mask settings and not the PAM's account and
	session management directives.
  * Mantis 0001627: omv_config_get returns wrong output.

 -- Volker Theile <volker.theile@openmediavault.org>  Wed, 12 Oct 2016 21:20:05 +0200

openmediavault (3.0.46) stable; urgency=low

  * Mantis 0001621: Fix erroneous smb.conf file.

 -- Volker Theile <volker.theile@openmediavault.org>  Wed, 12 Oct 2016 20:51:55 +0200

